Package author: Andy Salnikov

Please describe any modifications that you made to the package in the
reverse time order.

Tag: V00-13-05
2014-06-16 David Schneider
- rework epics store eventTag interface and logic
- add method to EpicsStoreImpl to get eventTag
	
Tag: V00-13-04
2014-06-05 David Schneider
- extend store for epics to take optional pvName. Bypasses internal maps that use 
  src and pvId to lookup name. Addresses trac ticket #305. 
- extend store for epics to take optional eventTag. Use tag to identify most
  recent TIME pv when pv comes from multiple sources. See comments in 
  track ticket #305. 
- trap for two different aliases to the same src/pvId pair. Keep first, discard others.

Tag: V00-13-03
2014-06-04 David Schneider
- Discards any epics alias that is also a epics pvname. Most such
  aliases are harmless (when they have the same name as the pv they alias).
  However sometimes they alias a different pv. This can be confusing
  and can mask the pv that has the same name as the alias.
  Addresses issues in trac tickets #304 #264 #234.

Tag: V00-13-02
2014-04-30 Mikhail Dubrovin
- in Env.h - fix doxygen documentation
	
Tag: V00-13-01
2014-02-27 Andy Salnikov
- forgot to implement PSEnv::jobNameSub()

Tag: V00-13-00
2014-02-26 Andy Salnikov
- preparing for multi-process psana
  - Env now has subprocess() and jobNameSub() methods
  - Env constructor takes subprocess id as an argument

Tag: V00-12-00
2014-01-13 Andy Salnikov
- environment now keeps an optional instance of alias map which has to
  be passed as a constructor argument

Tag: V00-11-04
2013-11-06 David Schneider
- use new ProxyDictHist from PSEvt in the configStore and calibStore

Tag: V00-11-03
2013-09-17 Andy Salnikov
- documentation generation changed in SConsTools, updating SConscript

Tag: V00-11-02
2013-03-27 Andy Salnikov
- fix for EpicsStore pvnames() method to remove duplicate names

Tag: V00-11-01
2013-03-14 Andy Salnikov
- Env class gets new method fwkName() which returns "psana" string

Tag: V00-11-00
